### Get all properties
GET http://localhost:5000/api/properties
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Get property by ID
GET http://localhost:5000/api/properties/{{property_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

###

### Create new property
POST http://localhost:5000/api/properties
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Modern Family Home in Bakersfield",
  "description": "Beautiful 3 bedroom home with backyard and pool.",
  "image": "https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1560185127-6ed189bf04bb",
  "price": 350000,
  "address": "123 Palm Street",
  "city": "Bakersfield",
  "propertyType": "House",
  "bedrooms": 3,
  "bathrooms": 2
}

###

### Update property
PUT http://localhost:5000/api/properties/{{property_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "price": 365000,
  "city": "Bakersfield"
}

###

### Delete property
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/properties/{{property_id}}

